import { Grid } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'
import {Wrapper} from './styled'

const DashboardLayout:React.FC = ({children}) =>{
    return <Wrapper container alignItems={'stretch'}>
        <Grid item md={2}>
            <Sidebar />
        </Grid>
        <Grid item md={10}>
            {children}
        </Grid>
    </Wrapper>
}
export default DashboardLayout
